responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "AF0A205E4AB377D4A1D1E6905B674DD0", "You were sent by Sehmi? The novice! He and his kin Harl have caused more trouble to the tribe than a horde of goblins! Still, these sherds do resonate some power. I will consult the Streamweavers, perhaps there is essence still within. You say you culled them from those addled cultists, the Sighted?")
